#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""PreCompact hook entry point - routes to front controller.

Runs before Claude Code runs a compact operation (manual via /compact or automatic
when context window is full). Use to control compaction behavior.

Official docs: https://code.claude.com/docs/en/hooks.md#precompact
"""
